### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Register (owner)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "03000000001",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "businessOwner",
  "name": "Owner One"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "03000000001",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Create business (set Bearer token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/businesses
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Restaurant",
  "type": "restaurant",
  "address": "Karachi",
  "lat": 24.8607,
  "lng": 67.0011
}

### Me
GET http://localhost:8080/api/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Addresses (add)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/me/addresses
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "home",
  "label": "Home",
  "address": "Block 6, PECHS, Karachi",
  "lat": 24.8607,
  "lng": 67.0011
}

### Addresses (select)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/me/addresses/home/select
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Upload stub
POST http://localhost:8080/api/uploads
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "product_image",
  "filename": "biryani.png",
  "contentType": "image/png"
}

### Save FCM token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/push-tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{fcmToken}}",
  "platform": "ios",
  "app": "customer"
}

### Test push (send to token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/push/test
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{fcmToken}}",
  "title": "BizzWay",
  "body": "Job near you (test)"
}

